{"pageProps":{"eyebrow":"eunomia-bpf","page":{"layout":"document","title":"ecli dockerfile usage","description":"bpf 运行时需要有Linux内核相关支持，docker 中的内核共享的宿主机的内核，因此使用docker运行bpf程序时需要使用以下命令为容器赋予权限和相关内核支持。","descriptionIsExcerpt":true,"bodyHtml":"<p>bpf 运行时需要有Linux内核相关支持，docker 中的内核共享的宿主机的内核，因此使用docker运行bpf程序时需要使用以下命令为容器赋予权限和相关内核支持。</p>\n<p>此处参考<a href=\"https://github.com/iovisor/bpftrace/blob/master/INSTALL.md#kernel-headers-install\">https://github.com/iovisor/bpftrace/blob/master/INSTALL.md#kernel-headers-install</a></p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">$</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> docker</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> run</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> -ti</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> -v</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> /usr/src:/usr/src:ro</span><span style=\"color:#F47067\"> \\</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\">       -v</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> /lib/modules/:/lib/modules:ro</span><span style=\"color:#F47067\"> \\</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\">       -v</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> /sys/kernel/debug/:/sys/kernel/debug:rw</span><span style=\"color:#F47067\"> \\</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\">       -v</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> /home/admin/my:/root/my</span><span style=\"color:#F47067\"> \\ </span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\">//挂载本机目录到容器的/root/my路径下</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">       --net</span><span style=\"color:#F47067\">=</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\">host</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\"> --pid</span><span style=\"color:#F47067\">=</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\">host</span><span style=\"color:#F69D50\"> --privileged</span><span style=\"color:#F47067\"> \\</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\">       ecli:1.0.1</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<h2 id=\"dockerfile-ubuntu\">dockerfile ubuntu</h2>\n<p>dockerfile的基础镜像是Ubuntu，国内使用时因为有墙的存在，所以需要对Linux进行换源。sources.list如下：</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">deb</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> jammy</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> main</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> restricted</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> universe</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> multiverse</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#768390\">#deb-src http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ jammy main restricted universe multiverse</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">deb</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> jammy-security</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> main</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> restricted</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> universe</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> multiverse</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#768390\">#deb-src http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ jammy-security main restricted universe multiverse</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">deb</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> jammy-updates</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> main</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> restricted</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> universe</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> multiverse</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#768390\">#deb-src http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ jammy-updates main restricted universe multiverse</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">deb</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> jammy-proposed</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> main</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> restricted</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> universe</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> multiverse</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#768390\">#deb-src http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ jammy-proposed main restricted universe multiverse</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">deb</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> jammy-backports</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> main</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> restricted</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> universe</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> multiverse</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#768390\">#deb-src http://mirrors.aliyun.com/ubuntu/ jammy-backports main restricted universe multiverse</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<p>dockerfile中的具体内容如下</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">FROM</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ubuntu:latest</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"> </span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">ENV</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> UBUNTU_SOURCE</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> /etc/apt</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"> </span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">COPY</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ./</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> /root</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"> </span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">WORKDIR</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> /root</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"> </span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">ADD</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> sources.list</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\"> $UBUNTU_SOURCE</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\">/</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"> </span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">RUN</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> apt-get</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> update</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\"> &#x26;&#x26; </span><span style=\"color:#F47067\">\\</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">    apt-get</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> -y</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> install</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> gcc</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> libelf-dev</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"> </span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#768390\">#CMD ./ecli run /root/my/package.json</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">CMD</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\"> [</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\">\"/bin/bash\"</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">]</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"> </span></code></pre></figure>\n<p>ubuntu.dockerfile构建时，同一级目录下的文件如下</p>\n<p><img src=\"/_content-assets/docs/img/image-20220905232754264.png\" alt=\"image-20220905232754264\"></p>\n<p>ecli可执行文件  sources.list Dockerfile这三个文件缺一不可，other文件可忽略。docker容器中wget无法连接外部网络，因此需要在docker构建时将ecli放入镜像中。使用镜像时只要挂载的本机目录中有package.json文件即可。</p>\n<h2 id=\"docker-alpine\">docker alpine</h2>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">FROM</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> alpine:latest</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"> </span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">COPY</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ./</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> /root</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"> </span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">WORKDIR</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> /root</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"> </span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">RUN</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> sed</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> -i</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> 's/dl-cdn.alpinelinux.org/mirrors.aliyun.com/g'</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> /etc/apk/repositories</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\"> &#x26;&#x26; </span><span style=\"color:#F47067\">\\</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">    apk</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> update</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\"> &#x26;&#x26; </span><span style=\"color:#F47067\">\\</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">    apk</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> install</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> gcc</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> libelf</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> gcompat</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"> </span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#768390\">#CMD ./ecli run /root/my/package.json</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<p>alpine.dockerfile构建镜像时，同一级目录下必须有ecli可执行文件。\n目前alpine.dockerfile仍存在以下问题</p>\n<p><img src=\"/_content-assets/docs/img/image-20220907195237651.png\" alt=\"image-20220907195237651\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"docker-build\">docker build</h3>\n<p>dockerfile构建时使用如下命令</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">sudo</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> docker</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> build</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> -t</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ecli:1.0.1</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> .</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<h3 id=\"参考文档\">参考文档</h3>\n<p>bpftrace 官方说明（如何让bpf程序在docker中运行）</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/iovisor/bpftrace/blob/master/INSTALL.md#kernel-headers-install\">https://github.com/iovisor/bpftrace/blob/master/INSTALL.md#kernel-headers-install</a></p>\n<p>如何在mac中运行带有bpf运行环境的docker</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://petermalmgren.com/docker-mac-bpf-perf/\">https://petermalmgren.com/docker-mac-bpf-perf/</a></p>","headings":[{"id":"dockerfile-ubuntu","text":"dockerfile ubuntu","depth":2},{"id":"docker-alpine","text":"docker alpine","depth":2},{"id":"docker-build","text":"docker build","depth":3},{"id":"参考文档","text":"参考文档","depth":3}],"sourcePath":"https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/eunomia.dev/tree/main/docs/eunomia-bpf/ecli/ecli-dockerfile-usage.zh.md","metadata":{"updatedAt":"2024-01-26T22:23:54.000Z","createdAt":"2023-08-10T12:54:12.000Z","authors":[{"name":"云微","email":"1067852565@qq.com"},{"name":"oluceps","email":"ospp@oluceps.uk"}]},"path":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecli/ecli-dockerfile-usage/","alternates":{"zh":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecli/ecli-dockerfile-usage/"},"continuation":{"index":{"title":"eunomia-bpf：简化并增强eBPF，支持CO-RE[^1]和WebAssembly[^2]","description":"![GitHub release (latest by date)](https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/eunomia-bpf/releases) ![codecov](https://codecov.io/gh/eunomia-bpf/eunomia-bpf) ![DeepSource](https://deepsource.io/gh/eunomia-bpf/eunomia-bpf/?ref=reposi","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/"},"previous":{"title":"ecc usage","description":"``sh ecc [OPTIONS] <SOURCEPATH [EXPORTEVENTHEADER] ``","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecc/usage/"},"next":{"title":"ecli","description":"ecli is the local eunomia-bpf CLI for loading, running, pulling, and pushing precompiled programs.","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecli/"}},"sidebar":[{"title":"eunomia-bpf：简化并增强eBPF，支持CO-RE[^1]和WebAssembly[^2]","items":[{"title":"eunomia-bpf：简化并增强eBPF，支持CO-RE[^1]和WebAssembly[^2]","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/","depth":0},{"title":"Project architecture","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/architecture/","depth":1},{"title":"benchmark","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/benchmark/","depth":1},{"title":"ecc docker usage","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecc/docker-usage/","depth":2},{"title":"github template","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecc/github-template/","depth":2},{"title":"eunomia-cc","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecc/","depth":1},{"title":"ecc usage","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecc/usage/","depth":2},{"title":"ecli dockerfile usage","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecli/ecli-dockerfile-usage/","depth":2},{"title":"ecli","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecli/","depth":1},{"title":"ecli server","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecli/server/","depth":2},{"title":"exporter","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/exporter/","depth":1},{"title":"usage","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/exporter/usage/","depth":2},{"title":"introduction","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/introduction/","depth":1},{"title":"eunomia-bpf 用户手册: 让 eBPF 程序的开发和部署尽可能简单","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/manual/","depth":1},{"title":"在线体验网站","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/online/","depth":1},{"title":"quickstart","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/quickstart/","depth":1},{"title":"build on android aarch64","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/setup/build-android-arm/","depth":2},{"title":"build from source","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/setup/build/","depth":2},{"title":"Install ecli and ecc","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/setup/","depth":1},{"title":"supporting-external-BTF","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/supporting-external-BTF/","depth":1},{"title":"video","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/video/","depth":1}]}]}},"__N_SSG":true}